  "tosSection1Title": "Acceptance of Voorwaarden",
  "tosSection1Para1": "By creating an account, accessing, or using the {appName} mobile application (\"the Service\"), you agree to be bound by these Voorwaarden of Service (\"TerVoorwaarden If you do not agree to these TVoorwaarden you must not access or use the Service.",
  "tosSection1Para2": "The Service is provided by {producer} (\"we\", \"us\", or \"our\"). These Voorwaarden form a legally binding agreement between you and us.",
  "tosSection2Title": "Eligibility & Account",
  "tosSection2Para1": "You must be at least 13 years old to use the Service. If you are under 18, you represent that your parent or legal guardian has read and agreed to these Voorwaarden on your behalf.",
  "tosSection2Para2": "You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for Alle activities that occur under your account. Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.",
  "tosSection3Title": "Gezondheid Information — Not Medical Advice",
  "tosSection3Para1": "{appName} is a Gezondheid companion application intended for informational and organizational purposes only. The Service is NOT a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations.",
  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI Triage feature provides general guidance based on the Symptomen you report. It is not a substitute for professional medical judgment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a medical eNoodgeval call your local Noodgeval number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do not rely on the Service for Noodgeval response.",
  "tosSection4Title": "Use of the Service",
  "tosSection4Intro": "You agree NOT to:",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "Use the Service for any unlawful purpose;",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble the app;",
  "tosSection4Bullet3": "Upload content that is malicious, fraudulent, or violates intellectual property rights;",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Anders users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Use the Service to send unsolicited communications or spam.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Subscriptions & Payments",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EOnderneming plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tVoorwaarden",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Annuleren your subscription at any Tijd through your platform's account sInstellingen",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will not apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Your Data",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Gezondheid data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Privacy Policy, which is incorporated into these Voorwaarden by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Exporteren your data at any Tijd via the in-app Exporteren feature, and you may permanently Verwijderen your account and Alle associated data via Instellingen → Verwijderen Account.",
  "tosSection7Title": "Disclaimers",
  "tosSection7Para1": "THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED \"AS IS\" AND \"AS AVAILABLE\" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, OR NON-INFRINGEMENT.",
  "tosSection7Para2": "We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, or that the AI Triage recommendations will be accurate or appropriate for your specific situation.",
  "tosSection8Title": "Limitation of Liability",
  "tosSection8Para1": "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, IN Nee EVENT SHALL {producer} BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF (OR INABILITY TO USE) THE SERVICE, WHETHER BASED ON WARRANTY, CONTRACT, TORT, OR ANY Anders LEGAL THEORY.",
  "tosSection9Title": "Termination",
  "tosSection9Para1": "You may stop using the Service and Verwijderen your account at any Tijd via SInstellingen We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service if you violate these Voorwaarden or if we reasonably believe we are Vereist to do so by law.",
  "tosSection9Para2": "Upon termination, Alle licenses granted to you will end, and your data will be deleted in accordance with our Privacy Policy.",
